room_title: Escape room "The Dark Sector" by North Valley Escape Room in Phoenix
room_address: 42302 N Vision Way, Suite 104, Anthem, AZ 85086
room_description:
You and your team of scientists have been assigned to a top-secret government facility on the moon where dangerous experiments are being tested. What has started off as a normal day has gone terribly bad... a hostile genetic experiment from the Dark Sector has escaped!
Lockdown of the facility will complete in one hour. Unfortunately, facility lockdown on the moon means complete annihilation. You and your team must complete a top-secret project to escape before you are either blown up... or eaten alive!
